### Tests API ClipRace - Fichier de test HTTP
### Utilisez ce fichier avec l'extension REST Client de VS Code

### Variables
@baseUrl = {{$dotenv NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL}}
@brandToken = {{$dotenv BRAND_TOKEN}}
@creatorToken = {{$dotenv CREATOR_TOKEN}}
@adminToken = {{$dotenv ADMIN_TOKEN}}
@contestId = 44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444

### =====================================================
### A - PRÉPARATION DES DONNÉES DE TEST
### =====================================================

### A1: Vérifier l'authentification brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}

### A2: Vérifier l'authentification creator
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### A3: Vérifier l'authentification admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### B - TESTS DE SOUMISSION
### =====================================================

### B1: Soumettre une vidéo (creator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TEST123",
  "platform": "youtube"
}

### B2: Tenter doublon (même vidéo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TEST123",
  "platform": "youtube"
}

### B3: Platform non autorisée
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://vine.co/v/INVALID",
  "platform": "vine"
}

### B4: URL malformée
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "not-a-valid-url",
  "platform": "youtube"
}

### B5: Tentative de soumission par brand (non autorisé)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BRAND123",
  "platform": "youtube"
}

### =====================================================
### C - TESTS DE SIGNATURE
### =====================================================

### C1: Signer une soumission (creator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/{{$dotenv SUBMISSION_ID}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accept_terms": true,
  "legal_name": "Jean Dupont"
}

### C2: Tenter de signer par brand (non autorisé)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/{{$dotenv SUBMISSION_ID}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accept_terms": true,
  "legal_name": "Brand User"
}

### C3: Signature sans accepter les termes
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/{{$dotenv SUBMISSION_ID}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accept_terms": false,
  "legal_name": "Jean Dupont"
}

### =====================================================
### D - TESTS RLS (Row Level Security)
### =====================================================

### D1: Creator accède à ses propres soumissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/submissions?creator_id=eq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### D2: Creator tente d'accéder aux soumissions d'autres creators
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/submissions?creator_id=neq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### D3: Brand accède aux soumissions de son contest
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/submissions?contest_id=eq.{{contestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}

### D4: Brand tente d'accéder aux soumissions d'autres contests
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/submissions?contest_id=neq.{{contestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}

### D5: Creator accède à ses messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/messages?or=(creator_id.eq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222,brand_id.eq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222)
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### D6: Creator tente d'accéder aux messages d'autres conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/messages?and=(creator_id.neq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222,brand_id.neq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222)
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### =====================================================
### E - TESTS DE STOCKAGE
### =====================================================

### E1: Tenter d'accéder à un fichier sans authentification
GET {{baseUrl}}/storage/v1/object/signatures/test.pdf

### E2: Lister les fichiers du bucket signatures (avec token admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/storage/v1/object/list/signatures
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY}}

### =====================================================
### F - TESTS DE PERFORMANCE
### =====================================================

### F1: Test de latence - Submit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contests/{{contestId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PERF1",
  "platform": "youtube"
}

### F2: Test de latence - Sign
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/submissions/{{$dotenv SUBMISSION_ID}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accept_terms": true,
  "legal_name": "Performance Test"
}

### =====================================================
### G - TESTS D'AUDIT ET NOTIFICATIONS
### =====================================================

### G1: Vérifier les logs d'audit (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/audit_logs?order=created_at.desc&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### G2: Vérifier les notifications du creator
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/notifications?user_id=eq.22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222&order=created_at.desc
Authorization: Bearer {{creatorToken}}

### G3: Vérifier les notifications du brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/notifications?user_id=eq.11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111&order=created_at.desc
Authorization: Bearer {{brandToken}}
